= SDL_SetSurfacePalette =
Use this function to set the palette used by a surface.


== Syntax ==
```c++
int SDL_SetSurfacePalette(SDL_Surface* surface,
                          SDL_Palette* palette)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''surface'''
|a pointer to the [[SDL_Surface]]
|-
|'''palette'''
|a pointer to the [[SDL_Palette]]
|}
